      <abstract label="Abstract:">Records of J.W. Spencer as chairman of the Administrative
        Board of the Laboratory of Ornithology include Administrative Board minutes,
        budgets, correspondence, and records about the search for a director. Also includes
        Bird-Watching Days Calendar and Postcards for Project Feeder Watch.</abstract>
      <langmaterial label="Language:">Collection material in <language encodinganalog="041" langcode="eng">English</language></langmaterial>
    </did>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
      <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
      <p>Records of J.W. Spencer as chairman of the Administrative Board of the Laboratory of
        Ornithology include Administrative Board minutes, budgets, correspondence, and
        records about the search for a director. Also includes Bird-Watching Days Calendar
        and Postcards for Project Feeder Watch.</p>
    </scopecontent>
